  <name>Fcitx5 Lekhika</name>
  <summary>Transliteration and autocorrection engine for Nepali Roman input</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Fcitx5 Lekhika is a plugin for the Fcitx5 input method framework. It provides
      smart transliteration from Romanized Nepali to Devanagari, along with
      autocorrection and dictionary-based learning features.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports Indic numerals, symbol transliteration, and customizable mappings.
    </p>
  </description>
